data.description: Luxury home on 2 acres!! This beautiful home offers the perfect family retreat!! The gorgeous salt water pool and waterfall, combined with a full outdoor kitchen makes this backyard truly an entertainer's dream! Inside the home is just as beautiful! As you enter into the 2 story foyer, you are greeted by a stunning wrought iron staircase, with your private office to the left, and formal dining on your right. Through the formal dining, you pass through an additional serving area across from the walk in pantry. Lots of cooks in the kitchen? No problem in this spacious and open kitchen, complete with a 5 burner gas stovetop, wall oven & microwave, and enough counter space for the grandest buffet! Spacious master offers a sitting area and a private courtyard area! Solitude awaits you in spa-like master bath area with jetted tub and separate vanities - and not 1, but 2 large closets so everyone has their own space! Send the kids upstairs where you will find a huge play/game room, 3 spacious bedrooms, and several closets lining the hallway! Bedroom #2 includes a private bath. Bedrooms 3 & 4 share a Jack & Jill bath, each with a private sink area.  This home has it all - both inside and out!! Updated with fresh paint throughout most of the home! Schedule your private showing today!
